OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mixed picture with occasional
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells through the day
OL,7,Fand further showers. Most of these
OL,8,Fwill be pretty light with one of two
OL,9,Fheavier downpours in the afternoon.
OL,10,FFeeling slightly warmer than Wednesday
OL,11,Fwith light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers continuing on places
OL,14,Fovernight, with the odd clear and dry
OL,15,Fspell. Milder than previous night with
OL,16,Fmost places staying above freezing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
