OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAnother mixed day with showers
OL,6,Fbut areas around the coast should
OL,7,Fremain dry. Showers heavier than of
OL,8,Flate with some brighter spells in
OL,9,Fbetween. Slighter warmer, especially
OL,10,Fin the south.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA wet
OL,13,Fstart to the weekend with some more
OL,14,Fshowers but turning drier into Sunday.
OL,15,FStaying mostly dry into the new week
OL,16,Fbut temperatures will start to drop.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
